      {
        "scenario": "OrderService down or slow (no circuit breaker)",
        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "Add a circuit breaker on CartService's OrderService call, mirroring the PaymentService pattern. Without it, OrderService degradation causes every checkout to burn 5s before failing, which under load will exhaust CartService's connection pool and cascade to all other CartService functionality."
